{
  "stem": "2533.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they-- well, you know, I don't know how they-- you know, that-- but in court, there was that many questions they asked.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had about six prosecutor, that man, and Frenzel had his lawyer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was an awful-- you know, even somebody else said once that if that lawyer would've been dressed in SS uniform, he would not have been better than-- than-- the way the questions and all that he was asking.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of a sudden, the judge came up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How did I know that the third camp had 27 people, because I mentioned that my brother was executed there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, I never said that there were-- I knew how many.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I only knew when they were executed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did I know it was-- you know, remember?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said-- And then I asked him in German, would you forget your mother's birthday?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, he was executed on my mother's birthday, the 27th of June.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had it all on paper, everything I said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I said to him, you have it all on paper, on tapes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I am getting old, older, old, and you want me to have every detail in my head when you have got it all in black and white?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He apologized.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But before that, there were other incidents in court.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Did I know who was shooting?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then I came just blankly I said to the translator, I said, do you want him to ask, or shall I ask him?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Would he look back when somebody was shooting at him?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, I was running for my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
